description:
Elder Marcus Mason talks about the unprecedented times we are living in and also the another pillar of our faith the Health Message. Once we realize the times, who is the last generation a most important question for us is how should we as Gods people be living in preparation to see Jesus in peace.

If the video will not play correctly please go to this link
https://www.apocalypseministries.org/aptv/

chapters.title: The Seventh Month Was Come and the Children of Israel Were in the Cities the People Gathered Themselves Together as One Man to Jerusalem
The Health Message Is the Right Arm of the Gospel

Their Strength of the Vital Powers and the Result Is a Deadening of the Sensibilities of the Mind It Goes On To Say and I Won't Read It all It Says Intemperance of any Kind Right but Numbs the Perceptive Organs and So Weakens the Brain Their Power that Eternal Things Are Not Appreciated so You Use that Was Why I Wanted To To Kind of Harp on that That Issue We Have with Diet because It's It's Kind of the First Thing Addressed in the Health Message Yes like You Said Now I Think that's a Beautiful Analogy of Leaving Egypt Going to Canaan Land Leaving Sin on Our Way to to Heaven or to Our Holy Life the First Thing God Dealt with Even before He Dealt with the Law So Much Is Given to Him He Began To Feed

You Know Brothers and Sisters as We'Re near the End of Time as We Are on the Precipice of the Crisis Which Means We'Re on the Precipice of Going to Heaven if We'Re Faithful this Is no Time To Let Our Hands Loosen on the Plows this Is no Time To Become Weary this Is no Time To Give Up this Is no Time To Begin To Doubt this Is no Time To Be Fearful It Is Time for Us To Lift Up Our Eyes toward Heaven from Which Cometh Our Strength It Is Time for Us To Understand that the Things We Are Experiencing Are the Things We Have Been Warned about and that Soon We Shall Have To Stand in the Sight of a Holy God with Our Mediator How Shall We Do these Things That God Is Requiring

As the Message of God while They Reject those Portions That Condemn Their Favorite Indulgences Such Persons Are Working Contrary to Their Own Welfare and the Welfare of the Church It Is Essential that We Walk in the Light while We Have the Light those Who Claim To Believe in Health Reform and Yet Work Counter to Its Principles in the Daily Life Practice Are Hurting Their Own Souls and Are Leaving Wrong Impressions upon the Minds of Believers and Unbelievers It Is High Time for Us To Do What God Has Access To Do by all Means We Must Seek God's Face for Help and Aid and Strength in Doing the Reforms

This Week as We Go Forward Let Us Spend Time with God Let Us Spend Time in His Word Let's Spend Time on Our Knees because in God's Mercy the Distractions Have Been Removed Spend Time with Christ Seek To Draw Closer to Him and Allow Him To Change You from Where You Are to Where He Wants You To Be Let's Have a Word of Prayer Father in Heaven Lord Were So Very Thankful for Your Love and Your Mercy for Your Word for the Spirit of Prophecy for the Reforms That You Have Given Us Lord To Show Us How To Become More like You Lord I Pray that the Hearts and Minds of those Who Have Been Listening
